{"tid":895388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭69歲老翁為結交女友 要求法院把年齡改成49歲","createTime":"2018-11-09T06:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T08:10:58.000Z","uid":83125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64faaf21945a9a3d556de8b2d259d17f9bfcbb6e","tid":895388,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】荷蘭一名老翁採取法律行動，要求把他的年齡降低20歲，藉以提高他結交女朋友的機會。拉泰爾班特表示他要求更改出生日期，就好像有些人要求變性一樣。預料法院將於四個星期內作出裁決。<br />\n<br />\n已屆69歲高齡的拉泰爾班特（Emile Ratelband）入稟阿姆斯特丹東南部阿納姆市法院，要求把他的出生日期由1949年3月11日，改為1969年3月11日。如果法院接納他的要求，他便會由69歲變成49歲。<br />\n<br />\n他接受荷蘭《電訊報》訪問時稱：「你可以改名，可以變性，那為甚麼不可以更改年歲？」<br />\n<br />\n拉泰爾班特稱，當他如實報上自己69歲時，處處受到限制，遭受年齡歧視，影響就業機會，<span style=\"color: red;\">也影響他用手機程式Tinder結交女朋友的機會。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7條野仲想搵SP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b360b292a940a56e15d19e02d08dfda605cfe3","tid":895388,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf9fc5c7a2768a2f9697ebfc6937a2cdefa43e7","tid":895388,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"睇相似49歲"},{"pid":"53b7c3ecf6c617eb8dc691808785928d418c8a35","tid":895388,"uid":189053,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a27a1f59a448742f63939a5301ba2269b76f84ef","tid":895388,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bf9fc5c7a2768a2f9697ebfc6937a2cdefa43e7","tid":895388,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"睇相似49歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"先去驗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b33af2fd6a17